snippet.title: Captain Claw - Level 1
snippet.description:
This short film shows passing through the 1st level of the best game ever. I wanted to approach everyone how to collect everything in La Roca. I lost a few coins, but they're not important.

The Claw Recluse site: http://kapitanpazur.piasta.pl/
